OL,3,CStudents training to teach 'priority'
OL,4,Csubjects to receive an extra #5,000
OL,6,FStudents training to teach 'priority'
OL,7,Fsubjects will receive an extra #5,000
OL,8,Fas part of the Welsh Government's new
OL,9,F100-day plan - but it's still #10,000
OL,10,Fshort of Plaid's manifesto promise.
OL,12,FThe scheme aims to attract those with
OL,13,Fa degree to complete the Initial
OL,14,FTeacher Education (ITE) programme in
OL,15,FWelsh, Science, Design and Technology,
OL,16,FComputer Science, Mathematics, and
OL,17,FInternational Languages.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G1/5
