CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F436A1781453487
OL,3,CStudents training to teach 'priority'
OL,4,Csubjects to receive an extra #5,000
OL,6,F"There appears to be no requirement
OL,7,Ffor teachers to work in schools for a
OL,8,Fcertain number of years following
OL,9,Ftheir induction to gain or retain
OL,10,Fthese benefits, and we know a
OL,11,Fsignificant proportion of teachers
OL,12,Fleave the profession within the first
OL,13,Ffive years of teaching."
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G4/5
