PN,43605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F436A1781453487
OL,3,CStudents training to teach 'priority'
OL,4,Csubjects to receive an extra #5,000
OL,6,FEducation Minister, Anna Brychan, said
OL,7,Fa sustainable teaching workforce is
OL,8,F"vital". She said: "We want to harness
OL,9,Fthe talent and skills we have here in
OL,10,FWales to achieve our ambitions for
OL,11,Feducation, ensuring that the money not
OL,12,Fonly supports people to train in
OL,13,FWales, but we also retain those skills
OL,14,Fto benefit learners across Wales."
OL,16,FFirst Minister, Rhun ap Iorwerth said
OL,17,Fthe incentive reflects their
OL,18,Fcommitment "to improving outcomes for
OL,19,Fteachers and pupils alike".
